PRE

Installed and working MPD, figlet and mpc

INSTALL 

Copy all files to ~/bin and make executable

Add ~/bin/now-playing-loop.sh to the end of ~/.profile

Set Pi to auto boot to text mode and login : https://raspberrypi.stackexchange.com/a/76275/42482 (basically, use raspi-config)

EXAMPLE IMAGE

https://twitter.com/thefalken/status/1456550808464629760/photo/1

